Show HN: Personalized Chatbot Therapist
text:
Greetings, esteemed members of Hacker News community!

I am thrilled to present my latest project - an innovative chatbot meticulously crafted to deliver tailored guidance and support for your mental well-being. Drawing from my in-depth research in psychology and self-help chatbots, I have spent several months actively training this bot to ensure it provides a truly exceptional experience.

To experience it firsthand, please visit https://minds.ee. The chatbot will offer personalized guidance and support, tailored to your specific requirements in a user-friendly and welcoming format.

As a strong proponent of providing access to resources that help prioritize mental well-being, I believe technology can play a pivotal role in achieving this goal. If you would like to learn more about my project or explore the chatbot further, please don't hesitate to reach out - I would be delighted to hear from you!
